content: The Proto-Amourworm is one of the many Key Items you can find in the latter half of Black Myth: Wukong, specifically within The Webbed Hollow. The item is incredibly important to Chen Loong's questline in The New West.

The content is as follows:
The Proto-Amourworm is one of the many Key Items you can find in the latter half of Black Myth: Wukong, specifically within The Webbed Hollow. The item is incredibly important to Chen Loong's questline in The New West.
